{"tid":2409512,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"胡錫進: 英國係美國嘅可憐應聲蟲","createTime":"2021-02-16T01:12:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-16T16:25:09.000Z","uid":229777,"like":3,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7410012200eeb3c4bfe4bba14c8dd7a51587979b","tid":2409512,"uid":229777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T01:12:31.000Z","msg":"挑機 <img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/plan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/plan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n近排支那轉風向打英國 <img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n英國真成美國的可憐應聲蟲了。在美國國家安全顧問沙利文表達對世衛專家組訪華報告&ldquo;深度擔憂&rdquo;之後，英國外交大臣拉布今天表示相同的&ldquo;擔憂&rdquo;。哈哈，現在這撥英國領導人生生把大英帝國變成了&ldquo;小英傀儡&rdquo;。還有澳大利亞，你出來。 ​​​<br />\n<br />\nSource: 佢微博 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6865dfd24f40a1f5b9ffb59d72e7a4cf1ef41dd3","tid":2409512,"uid":82312,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T01:17:09.000Z","msg":"粗暴干預別國內政"},{"pid":"33e0161bcbfbb24fe3a78972446cdf52fb278661","tid":2409512,"uid":201027,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T01:18:20.000Z","msg":"厲害了我的國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0f877e0ee629840f39e85bfd5e7187cea605bbc","tid":2409512,"uid":229777,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"6865dfd24f40a1f5b9ffb59d72e7a4cf1ef41dd3","tid":2409512,"uid":82312,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T01:17:09.000Z","msg":"粗暴干預別國內政"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T01:18:27.000Z","msg":"支那不嬲都干預別國內政 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d48bcc87e637ee086347d1b89b8348aa9bbf8da","tid":2409512,"uid":229777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"33e0161bcbfbb24fe3a78972446cdf52fb278661","tid":2409512,"uid":201027,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T